"fields\":[],\"serviceId\":\"/_api/modelPhysicModelDraft/update/cascade/{modelNames}\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"data\":\"{}\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":[{\"key\":\"{modelNames}\",\"value\":\"\"}],\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\n    // 通过 vars.params 可以更改查询参数\\n    // 通过 vars.data 可以更改requestdata\\n    // 通过 config.header 可以更改 header\\n    // 通过 config.url 可以更改  url\\n    /* vars.data = {\\n    } */\\n    // console.log(vars, config);\\n    // 可以查看还有哪些参数可以修改。\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\n    // data.data.b = 1; 修改返回数据结构中的 b 字段为1\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\n    // console.log(error);\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\n}\",\"methodType\":\"POST\",\"description\":\"物理模型草稿更新指定的一对多对象\",\"methodName\":\"updateCascadeSpecific\",\"type\":\"model\",\"url\":\"/_api/modelPhysicModelDraft/update/cascade/{modelNames}\"},{\"name\":\"createCascade\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"label\":\"物理模型草稿\",\"descr\":\"保存一对多的对象\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"autoLoad\":true,\"loadType\":\"1\",\"fields\":[],\"serviceId\":\"/_api/modelPhysicModelDraft/create/cascade\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"data\":\"{}\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":[],\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\n    // 通过 vars.params 可以更改查询参数\\n    // 通过 vars.data 可以更改requestdata\\n    // 通过 config.header 可以更改 header\\n    // 通过 config.url 可以更改  url\\n    /* vars.data = {\\n    } */\\n    // console.log(vars, config);\\n    // 可以查看还有哪些参数可以修改。\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\n    // data.data.b = 1; 修改返回数据结构中的 b 字段为1\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\n    // console.log(error);\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\n}\",\"methodType\":\"POST\",\"description\":\"物理模型草稿保存一对多的对象\",\"methodName\":\"createCascade\",\"type\":\"model\",\"url\":\"/_api/modelPhysicModelDraft/create/cascade\"}]}],\"services\":[{\"name\":\"loadModelArch\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"载入模型目录树\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"79891417828397056\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.workspaceIds = $this.workspaceId;\\r\\n    vars.params.teamName = $identity.teamName;\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    if (data.data.length === 0) {\\r\\n        return data.data;\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    $this.setModelTree(data.data[0].children);\\r\\n    const expandFunc = function (arr, map) {\\r\\n        arr.forEach(item => {\\r\\n            map[item.key] = item;\\r\\n            if (item.children) {\\r\\n                expandFunc(item.children, map);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        });\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    const getDirArr = function (arr, map, dirId) {\\r\\n        if (map[dirId]) {\\r\\n            arr.unshift(dirId);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        if (map[dirId] && map[dirId].parentId) {\\r\\n            getDirArr(arr, map, map[dirId].parentId);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    const findLvl = function (key, map) {\\r\\n        if (map[key]) {\\r\\n            if (map[key].type == 'lvl') {\\r\\n                $this.setArchLvl(map[key].archCode);\\r\\n                if (!$this.modelId) {\\r\\n                    $this.setFormData({ lvl: map[key].archCode });\\r\\n                    $this.datasourceMap.resolveNamingRule();\\r\\n                }\\r\\n            } else if (map[key].parentId) {\\r\\n                findLvl(map[key].parentId, map);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    const findTopic = function (key, map) {\\r\\n        if (map[key]) {\\r\\n            if (map[key].type == 'topic') {\\r\\n                $this.setArchTopic(map[key].archCode);\\r\\n                if (!$this.modelId) {\\r\\n                    $this.setFormData({ topic: map[key].archCode });\\r\\n                }\\r\\n            } else if (map[key].parentId) {\\r\\n                findTopic(map[key].parentId, map);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    const keyMap = {};\\r\\n    expandFunc(data.data[0].children, keyMap);\\r\\n    if ($this.dirId) {\\r\\n        if (!keyMap[$this.dirId]) {\\r\\n            $this.setDirId('');\\r\\n            $this.utils.modal.warning({\\r\\n                title: '警告',\\r\\n                content:\\r\\n                    '模型归属目录ID“' + $this.dirId + '”错误，请重新选择！',\\r\\n            });\\r\\n        } else {\\r\\n            const curArr = [];\\r\\n            getDirArr(curArr, keyMap, $this.dirId);\\r\\n            $this.$refs.baseForm.formRef.current.setFieldsValue({ dirIdArr: curArr });\\r\\n            findLvl($this.dirId, keyMap);\\r\\n            findTopic($this.dirId, keyMap);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadLvlOptions();\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadTopicOptions();\\r\\n    return data.data[0].children; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    console.error(error);\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"getModel\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"获取模型数据\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"/_api/modelPhysicModelDraft/{id}\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    config.url=config.url.replace('{id}',$this.modelId);\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(true);\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(false);\\r\\n    const targetData = { ...data.data };\\r\\n    if (targetData.extendItems) {\\r\\n        targetData.extendItems = JSON.parse(targetData.extendItems);\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    $this.setFormData(targetData);\\r\\n    $this.setDirId(targetData.dirId);\\r\\n    $this.setWorkspaceId(targetData.workspaceId);\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadModelArch();\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.resolveNamingRule();\\r\\n    //模型类型回显\\r\\n    const expandFunc = function (arr, map) {\\r\\n        arr.forEach(item => {\\r\\n            map[item.value] = item;\\r\\n            if (item.children) {\\r\\n                expandFunc(item.children, map);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        });\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadModelTypeOptions();\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadSensLvlOptions();\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(false);\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"saveModel\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"保存模型\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"l4864532203474944\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    //从父页面表单取数据\\r\\n    const saveData = {...$this.formData};\\r\\n\\r\\n    saveData.devDirId = $this.devDirId;\\r\\n\\r\\n    saveData.logicModelId = saveData.logicModelId||$this.logicModelId||'';\\r\\n    \\r\\n    saveData.updateUser = $identity.userId;\\r\\n    if(!$this.modelId){\\r\\n        saveData.createUser = $identity.userId;\\r\\n        saveData.teamName = $identity.teamName;\\r\\n        saveData.memberName = $identity.teamName+'-'+$identity.userId;\\r\\n    }\\r\\n\\r\\n    //二次编辑需要带上模型ID\\r\\n    if($this.modelId){\\r\\n        saveData.id = $this.modelId;\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    if($this.workspaceId) {\\r\\n        saveData.workspaceId = $this.workspaceId;\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    //从目录级联框取模型归属目录ID\\r\\n    if(saveData.dirIdArr&&saveData.dirIdArr.length>0){\\r\\n        saveData.dirId = saveData.dirIdArr[saveData.dirIdArr.length-1];\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    //从模型类型级联框取模型类型编码\\r\\n    if(saveData.modelTypeArr&&saveData.modelTypeArr.length>0){\\r\\n        saveData.modelType = saveData.modelTypeArr[saveData.modelTypeArr.length-1];\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    //从层次级联框取模型层次编码\\r\\n    if(saveData.lvlArr&&saveData.lvlArr.length>0){\\r\\n        saveData.lvl = saveData.lvlArr[saveData.lvlArr.length-1];\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    //从主题级联框取模型主题编码\\r\\n    if(saveData.topicArr&&saveData.topicArr.length>0){\\r\\n        saveData.topic = saveData.topicArr[saveData.topicArr.length-1];\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    //取命名参数\\r\\n    saveData.extendItems = JSON.stringify(saveData.extendItems);\\r\\n\\r\\n    //去掉多余的属性\\r\\n    delete saveData.dirIdArr;\\r\\n    delete saveData.modelTypeArr;\\r\\n    delete saveData.lvlArr;\\r\\n    delete saveData.topicArr;\\r\\n\\r\\n    //组装各个tab页中的数据\\r\\n    saveData.modelPhysicModelFieldDraftList = $this.fields;\\r\\n\\r\\n    //物化信息\\r\\n    $this.$refs.cfgTabs.state.tabs.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (item.key === $this.dsType + 'PhysicInfo') {\\r\\n            try{\\r\\n                if ($this.getChildren($this.dsType + 'PhysicInfo') && $this.getChildren($this.dsType + 'PhysicInfo').formData) {\\r\\n                saveData.extendItems = JSON.stringify($this.getChildren($this.dsType + 'PhysicInfo').formData);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n            }catch(e){\\r\\n                console.error(e);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n\\r\\n    //校验当前tab页，并取最新数据\\r\\n    switch($this.$refs.cfgTabs.state.activeTab) {\\r\\n        case 'fields':\\r\\n            saveData.modelPhysicModelFieldDraftList = $this.getChildren('fields').formData.fields;\\r\\n            break;\\r\\n\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    saveData.modelPhysicModelFieldDraftList.forEach(field=>{\\r\\n        if(field.length){\\r\\n            field.length = field.length+'';\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        if(field.precisionVal){\\r\\n            field.precisionVal = field.precisionVal+'';\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    vars.data = saveData;\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(true);\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(false);\\r\\n    //回填模型ID供二次编辑使用\\r\\n    $this.setModelId(data.data.id);\\r\\n    $utils.notification.success({\\r\\n        title: '成功',\\r\\n        content: '模型保存成功！',\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    if($this.getParent()){\\r\\n        $this.close();\\r\\n        if($this.getParent().datasourceMap&&$this.getParent().datasourceMap.getModelPage){\\r\\n            $this.getParent().datasourceMap.getModelPage();\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        if($this.getParent().datasourceMap&&$this.getParent().datasourceMap.getArchTree){\\r\\n            $this.getParent().datasourceMap.getArchTree();\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(false);\\r\\n    $utils.notification.error({\\r\\n        title: '保存失败',\\r\\n        content: '模型保存失败！',\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\",\"callback\":\"\"},{\"name\":\"loadLvlOptions\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"载入层次选项信息\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"90019170187710464\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.subjectName='lvl';\\r\\n    vars.params.workspaceId=$this.workspaceId;\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    const roots = [];\\r\\n    const idMap = {};\\r\\n    const idNameMap = {};\\r\\n    const nameIdMap = {};\\r\\n\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (!item.parentId) {\\r\\n            roots.push(item);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        idMap[item.id] = item;\\r\\n        idNameMap[item.id] = item.subjectName;\\r\\n        nameIdMap[item.subjectName] = item.id;\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (item.parentId && idMap[item.parentId]) {\\r\\n            if (!idMap[item.parentId].children) {\\r\\n                idMap[item.parentId].children = [];\\r\\n            }\\r\\n            idMap[item.parentId].children.push(item);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    $this.setLvlOptions(roots);\\r\\n    if ($this.formData.lvl) {\\r\\n        const getSubjectArr = function (arr, map, id, idNameMap) {\\r\\n            if(map[id]){\\r\\n                arr.unshift(idNameMap[id]);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n            if (map[id] && map[id].parentId) { \\r\\n                getSubjectArr(arr, map, map[id].parentId, idNameMap);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        const curArr = [];\\r\\n        getSubjectArr(curArr, idMap, nameIdMap[$this.formData.lvl], idNameMap);\\r\\n        $this.$refs.baseForm.formRef.current.setFieldsValue({lvlArr:curArr});\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"loadTopicOptions\",\"stateName\":\"topicOptions\",\"descr\":\"载入主题选项信息\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"90019170187710464\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.subjectName='topic';\\r\\n    vars.params.workspaceId=$this.workspaceId;\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    const roots = [];\\r\\n    const idMap = {};\\r\\n    const idNameMap = {};\\r\\n    const nameIdMap = {};\\r\\n\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (!item.parentId) {\\r\\n            roots.push(item);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        idMap[item.id] = item;\\r\\n        idNameMap[item.id] = item.subjectName;\\r\\n        nameIdMap[item.subjectName] = item.id;\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (item.parentId && idMap[item.parentId]) {\\r\\n            if (!idMap[item.parentId].children) {\\r\\n                idMap[item.parentId].children = [];\\r\\n            }\\r\\n            idMap[item.parentId].children.push(item);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    $this.setTopicOptions(roots);\\r\\n    if ($this.formData.topic) {\\r\\n        const getSubjectArr = function (arr, map, id, idNameMap) {\\r\\n            if(map[id]){\\r\\n                arr.unshift(idNameMap[id]);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n            if (map[id] && map[id].parentId) { \\r\\n                getSubjectArr(arr, map, map[id].parentId, idNameMap);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        const curArr = [];\\r\\n        getSubjectArr(curArr, idMap, nameIdMap[$this.formData.topic], idNameMap);\\r\\n        $this.$refs.baseForm.formRef.current.setFieldsValue({topicArr:curArr});\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"resolveNamingRule\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"90126841020649472\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.data.lvl = $this.formData.lvl;\\r\\n    vars.data.workspaceId = $this.workspaceId;\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    const namingComs = { layout: 'inline', fields: [] };\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        let com = {};\\r\\n        if (item.defValue) {\\r\\n            com = { label: item.defValue };\\r\\n        } else if (item.recComponent == 'select') {\\r\\n            com = { field: item.field, label: item.recRule, noStyle: true, mapProp: item.mapProp };\\r\\n            com.type = 'select';\\r\\n            com.options = {\\r\\n                placeholder: item.recRule,\\r\\n                options: item.options,\\r\\n                type: 'button'\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        } else if (item.recComponent == 'cascader') {\\r\\n            com = { field: item.field, label: item.recRule, noStyle: true, mapProp: item.mapProp };\\r\\n            com.type = 'cascader';\\r\\n            com.options = {\\r\\n                placeholder: item.recRule,\\r\\n                options: item.options\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        } else if (item.recComponent == 'input') {\\r\\n            com = { field: item.field, label: item.recRule, noStyle: true, mapProp: item.mapProp };\\r\\n            com.type = 'input';\\r\\n            com.options = {\\r\\n                placeholder: item.recRule,\\r\\n                \\\"onChange\\\": function callback(val) {\\r\\n                    \\r\\n                }\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        if (item.mapProp && $this.formData[item.mapProp]) {\\r\\n            const target = { ...$this.formData };\\r\\n            target.extendItems = { ...$this.formData.extendItems };\\r\\n            target.extendItems[item.field] = $this.formData[item.mapProp];\\r\\n            $this.setFormData(target);\\r\\n\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        namingComs.fields.push(com);\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    $this.setNamingComs(namingComs);\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"loadModelTypeOptions\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"载入模型类型选项信息\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"121952148195086336\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.subjectName='logicModelType';\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    const roots = [];\\r\\n    const idMap = {};\\r\\n    const valueMap = {};\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        valueMap[item.subjectName] = item;\\r\\n        idMap[item.id] = item;\\r\\n        if (!item.parentId) {\\r\\n            roots.push(item);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    data.data.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (item.parentId && idMap[item.parentId]) {\\r\\n            item.parentName = idMap[item.parentId].subjectName;\\r\\n            if (!idMap[item.parentId].children) {\\r\\n                idMap[item.parentId].children = [];\\r\\n            }\\r\\n            idMap[item.parentId].children.push(item);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    $this.setModelTypeOptions(roots);\\r\\n\\r\\n    if ($this.formData.modelType) {\\r\\n        const getModelTypeArr = function (arr, map, dirId) {\\r\\n            arr.unshift(dirId);\\r\\n            if (map[dirId] && map[dirId].parentName) {\\r\\n                getModelTypeArr(arr, map, map[dirId].parentName);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        const curArr = [];\\r\\n        getModelTypeArr(curArr, valueMap, $this.formData.modelType);\\r\\n        $this.$refs.baseForm.formRef.current.setFieldsValue({ modelTypeArr: curArr });\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"loadSensLvlOptions\",\"stateName\":\"sensLvlOptions\",\"descr\":\"载入敏感级别选项信息\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"121952148195086336\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.subjectName = 'SENS_LVL';\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    $this.setTableInfoLoaded(true);\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"loadCycleTypeOptions\",\"stateName\":\"cycleTypeOptions\",\"descr\":\"载入周期选项信息\",\"autoLoad\":true,\"serviceId\":\"121952148195086336\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.subjectName='cycleType';\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    // data.data.b = 1; 修改返回数据结构中的 b 字段为1\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"loadDsOptions\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"获取数据源选项\",\"autoLoad\":true,\"serviceId\":\"80305156188770304\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.dsCategory = 'rdb,mpp,hive,redis,kafka,hbase,redis,mq,sqlfire,gemfirexd,aster,teradata,es,opentsdb,hdfs';\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    $this.setDsOptions(data.data);\\r\\n    if ($this.formData.dsName) {\\r\\n        const targetDs = data.data.filter(item => {\\r\\n            return item.name == $this.formData.dsName;\\r\\n        });\\r\\n        if (targetDs.length > 0) {\\r\\n            $this.setDsType(targetDs[0].dsType);\\r\\n            $this.datasourceMap.getSubjects();\\r\\n            const targetSchemas = [];\\r\\n            targetDs[0].schemas.forEach(item => {\\r\\n                targetSchemas.push({\\r\\n                    value: item,\\r\\n                    label: item\\r\\n                });\\r\\n            });\\r\\n            $this.setSchemaOptions(targetSchemas);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"getSubjects\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"/_api/modelSubjectItem/search/cascade\",\"method\":\"get\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    vars.params.itemName=$this.dsType+'FieldDataType';\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    data.data.content.forEach(item => {\\r\\n        if (item.itemName == $this.dsType + 'FieldDataType') {\\r\\n            $this.setDataTypeOptions(item.modelSubjectList);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    });\\r\\n    \\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"},{\"name\":\"getLogicModel\",\"stateName\":\"\",\"descr\":\"获取逻辑模型数据\",\"autoLoad\":false,\"serviceId\":\"/_api/modelLogicModelDraft/{id}\",\"method\":\"GET\",\"dataBindVar\":\"\",\"placeholders\":\"[]\",\"condition\":true,\"conditionBindVar\":\"\",\"before\":\"function beforeCallback(vars, config) {\\r\\n    config.url=config.url.replace('{id}',$this.logicModelId);\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(true);\\r\\n}\",\"success\":\"function successCallback(data) {\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(false);\\r\\n    const targetData = { ...data.data };\\r\\n    delete targetData.id;\\r\\n    targetData.modelPhysicModelFieldDraftList = targetData.modelLogicModelFieldDraftList;\\r\\n    if (targetData.extendItems) {\\r\\n        targetData.extendItems = JSON.parse(targetData.extendItems);\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    $this.setFormData(targetData);\\r\\n    $this.setDirId(targetData.dirId);\\r\\n    $this.setWorkspaceId(targetData.workspaceId);\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadModelArch();\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.resolveNamingRule();\\r\\n    //模型类型回显\\r\\n    const expandFunc = function (arr, map) {\\r\\n        arr.forEach(item => {\\r\\n            map[item.value] = item;\\r\\n            if (item.children) {\\r\\n                expandFunc(item.children, map);\\r\\n            }\\r\\n        });\\r\\n    }\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadModelTypeOptions();\\r\\n    $this.datasourceMap.loadSensLvlOptions();\\r\\n    return data.data; // 重要，需返回 data\\r\\n}\",\"fail\":\"function failCallback(error){\\r\\n    $this.setLoading(false);\\r\\n    // console.log(error);\\r\\n    // 可以在这里做弹框提示等操作\\r\\n}\"}],\"i18n\":{\"zh-CN\":\"{}\",\"en-US\":\"\"}},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"56cf453b1136e074\",\"name\":\"56cf453b1136e074\",\"label\":\"flex布局\",\"type\":\"flexLayout\",\"options\